item.title: Typing Fighter
item.description: Type fast, type accurate and fight hard in this innovative street fighter style typing game. Charge up your typing and deliver killer power moves. Get inspired by motivational phrases and quotes while you type. Fight against a variety of opponents. Features: Beautifully designed street fight urban setting Fluid character animations Over 200 motivational quotes and phrases to keep you going
